IN RE Application of DAYTON POWER & LIGHT CO. 2017-0204 Supreme Court of Ohio. November 28, 2018

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

Sua sponte, appeal dismissed as moot. O'CONNOR, C.J., and KENNEDY, FISCHER, and DEWINE, JJ., concur. O'DONNELL and FRENCH, JJ., dissent. DEGENARO, J., not participating.
